A weathered golden retriever with distinguished gray around its muzzle sits attentively at an old wooden desk, wearing vintage reading glasses perched on its nose. Before the dog sits an antique mechanical typewriter with wisps of steam rising from it, transformed with brass gears and copper pipes in steampunk fashion. The dog's paw rests confidently on the typewriter keys. Behind the scene, a massive wall of interconnected clockwork mechanisms, pressure gauges, and glowing vacuum tubes hums with energy. Warm amber light from Edison bulbs casts dramatic shadows across the scene. The atmosphere blends Victorian industrial aesthetics with a sense of discovery and adaptation. Scattered around the desk are rolled blueprints and brass instruments. The color palette emphasizes rich browns, burnished copper, deep teals, and warm golden highlights. Vintage steampunk style with intricate mechanical details and atmospheric lighting.
